Anix continued along the bank, her internal computer trying to hone in on 
any local Preds.

"Hmm, there's something over here..." Anix rounds a bend in the stream and 
stops short as she sees the damaged land cruiser floating in the water.

"Definitely Predacons, I wonder how many. Computer, how many Predacon 
signatures are there?"

*Unable to comply, scanners at 15% and dropping, revert to beast mode.*

Anix sighed, "beast mode." She continued to crawl towards the ship, watching 
for any sign of Preds.
